00:26:41.854 --> 00:26:46.437
please. escort this evil being.
walk him out of my town.

503
00:26:46.521 --> 00:26:47.521
[nostalgic music swells]

504
00:26:47.604 --> 00:26:50.354
Please call all
the people in the town… [huffs]

505
00:26:51.062 --> 00:26:54.604
[groans] Tell them I asked them
to take all calamities. [groans]

506
00:26:54.687 --> 00:26:55.896
all losses.

507
00:26:56.479 --> 00:26:58.396
struggles. [groans]

508
00:26:58.479 --> 00:27:00.562
all the woes. [heaving]

509
00:27:00.646 --> 00:27:03.146
all that has to do
with suffering in my town.

510
00:27:03.229 --> 00:27:05.312
should be used to drive him
out of this town.

511
00:27:05.396 --> 00:27:08.521
You must never set foot
in this town again.

512
00:27:08.604 --> 00:27:11.187
[whines]

513
00:27:11.812 --> 00:27:16.062
[birds chirping]

514
00:27:21.521 --> 00:27:23.771
[screams]

515
00:27:25.687 --> 00:27:27.812
