525
00:27:56.229 --> 00:27:58.229
♪ Esusu. you have to leave our town. ♪

526
00:27:58.312 --> 00:27:59.979
♪ We no longer want you here ♪

527
00:28:00.062 --> 00:28:01.979
♪ Esusu. you have to leave our town. ♪

528
00:28:02.062 --> 00:28:05.062
♪ We no longer want you here.
